title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show JUN-04-2014 WED
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show JUN-04-2014 WED...PODCAST


The Glenn Beck Program


 The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm 



        
      
      Michelle Malkin and Marcus Luttrell join Glenn to discuss
           the strange Bowe Bergdahl 

      6/04/14Wednesday, June 04, 2014


Facebook: Glenn Beck
Twitter: @glennbeck

Glenn covers last night's election results,

 goes over the details and deaths in trying to find Bowe Bergdahl
   with Michelle Malkin and speaks with Marcus Luttrell 
    about his experience in Afghanistan and his thoughts on Bowe Bergdahl.

 Also, Chris McDaniel joins Glenn from Mississippi. 


        That and more on The Glenn Beck Program!
